summary: Completed comprehensive frontend UI testing of Sitesellr e-commerce platform. All major features and pages tested successfully. Landing page, auth pages, admin dashboard, and all admin sections (Products, Orders, Customers, Store Builder, Marketing, Analytics, Settings) are working perfectly with mock data.
passed_tests: Landing page loads with hero section, features, pricing, testimonials, FAQ
Navigation links work correctly (Features, Pricing, Testimonials, FAQ)
Login page loads with all form elements (email, password, remember me, social login)
Register page loads with all required form elements
Admin dashboard loads after login simulation
Dashboard displays stats cards (4), revenue chart, category chart, recent orders, activity feed
All admin pages accessible via sidebar navigation (Products, Orders, Customers, Store Builder, Marketing, Analytics, Settings)
Products page shows product table with images, SKUs, categories, prices, stock status
Orders page displays order management interface with status tracking
Customers page shows customer relationship management features
Store Builder page displays theme selection with 6 themes (3 free, 3 pro)
Settings page shows multiple configuration tabs
Theme toggle (dark/light mode) works on all pages
User menu and notifications dropdown function properly
All form controls are interactive and functional
